column2: SELECT   b.ra as lam_ra,b.dec as lam_dec,   a.ra as SDSS_ra,a.dec as SDSS_dec, a.petroMag_u, a.petroMag_g , a.petroMag_r , a.petroMag_i , a.petroMag_z into mydb.cross_petroMag_dr5 from mydb.cross_dr5 as b   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(b.ra,b.dec,#) as c   JOIN DR1#.PhotoObjAll as a ON c.objid = a.objid
